[{"c":"<p>Sweet hour of prayer</p><p>Sweet hour of prayer</p><p>That calls me from a world of care</p><p>And bids me at my Father's throne</p><p>Make all my wants and wishes known</p><p>In seasons of distress and grief</p><p>My soul has often found relief</p><p>And oft escaped the tempter's snare</p><p>By Thy return, sweet hour of prayer</p>"},{"c":"<p>Sweet hour of prayer</p><p>Sweet hour of prayer</p><p>The joys I feel, the bliss I share</p><p>Of those whose anxious spirits burn</p><p>With strong desires for Thy return</p><p>With such I hasten to the place</p><p>Where God my Savior shows His face</p><p>And gladly take my station there</p><p>And wait for Thee, sweet hour of prayer</p>"},{"c":"<p>Sweet hour of prayer! sweet hour of prayer!</p><p>thy wings shall my petition bear</p><p>to him whose truth and faithfulness</p><p>engage the waiting soul to bless.</p><p>And since he bids me seek his face,</p><p>believe his word, and trust his grace,</p><p>I'll cast on him my every care,</p><p>and wait for thee, sweet hour of prayer!</p>"},{"c":"<p>Sweet hour of prayer! sweet hour of prayer!</p><p>May I thy consolation share,</p><p>Till, from Mount Pisgah’s lofty height,</p><p>I view my home and take my flight.</p><p>This robe of flesh I’ll drop, and rise</p><p>To seize the everlasting prize,</p><p>And shout, while passing through the air,</p><p>“Farewell, farewell, sweet hour of prayer!”</p>"}]